  "bookId": 68,
  "firstAcquaintance": "The gentle former wanderer group leader is feeling a bit hot-tempered toward enemies today. She walks pigeon-toed, as if enduring something.",
  "personality": "For some reason, Makusu is more absent-minded than usual today and not quite herself. But that bashful demeanor makes her seem even more adorable.",
  "like": "Making milk-based dishes",
  "familiarData": "Female minotaurs begin producing milk from their breasts at a certain age. Normally the amount is modest, but during the lactation period their breasts enlarge and produce much more milk.\nMakusu's past life of drifting from place to place meant she never truly experienced a full lactation period, though she noticed she leaked milk more easily at certain times.\nAfter coming to the guildhall and enjoying stable meals, Makusu noticed her body becoming fuller and leaking more readily. Now, she finally feels the intensity of the lactation period -- even slight movement leaves her chest damp, and a little squeeze can fill an entire jar.\nMakusu's lineage is from the cow clan within the minotaur race, a subspecies bred specifically for milk production, so her lactation periods are far more intense than anyone else's.\nConfronted with this sudden onset of lactation, a bewildered Makusu has no choice but to ask her beloved master to help her deal with the endlessly flowing milk.",
